{"tid":422232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［冇圖］原來宜家啲菜街大媽可以連斑馬線都霸埋","createTime":"2017-10-03T01:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T01:36:34.000Z","uid":15849,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e20141b74534715251c238d4b36a3556448fb97c","tid":422232,"uid":15849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"本身已經因為班煩膠賣淫大媽唔想再行菜街。<br />\n呢兩日有事經過，見到有檔大媽檔竟然將個檔口開到去荷李活對出條斑馬線上面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/092711_2c6f8bbecb2af1c546b0d7b0e3a61088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F092711_2c6f8bbecb2af1c546b0d7b0e3a61088.jpg&h=a1fb03f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/092712_f9335c07017978b17b66fbc41d2a7d24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F092712_f9335c07017978b17b66fbc41d2a7d24.jpg&h=40c7501c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我仆你個臭街，見到個大媽個樣惡撚到好似淨係霸咗你一半行人路係蝕撚咗比你咁。<br />\n<br />\n期間有個警犬行過去，話「又點嘛⋯⋯」之後太細聲聽唔到，斷估都係又有路人投訴個大媽。<br />\n<br />\n而結果呢？警犬講咗兩句個大媽唔show佢然後自己走撚咗企埋一邊。我屌你老母呀！"},{"pid":"f6aef7dbcf021ebad2a04ecbb7883f4c4a57e890","tid":422232,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:35:57.000Z","msg":"點解而家旺角冇人扔強水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba9a48ac092f84958b8653f3da00f2e1e1d4550","tid":422232,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:36:34.000Z","msg":"大你老母媽"}]}